description:
LocalAccessM:  Table storing metadata about local access network elements, including identification, location, and emergency restoration configuration.

dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (appears to be the same as CellId).
Id3:  Ancillary identifier (always '1' in this sample).
Id4: Ancillary identifier (always '1' in this sample).
vsDataType: Data type identifier (constant 'vsDataLocalAccessM').
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format (constant 'EricssonSpecificAttributes').
LocalAccessM.emergencyRestore: Emergency restoration strategy (e.g., 'PHYSICALONLY').
LocalAccessM.localAccessMId:  Unique identifier for the local access element.
LocalAccessM.userLabel: User-defined label (appears to be empty in this sample).
